      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, making it a fantastic choice for anyone seeking dependable performance! It drives smoothly and looks great, showing only the minor signs of use you'd expect from a well-loved car. Ready for many more miles of adventure!",
